<%= render "mailers/shared/header",
    title: "Action Required: 1 Hour Left",
    company_name: "My Custom Sleep Journey" %>

<div style="padding: 0 30px 20px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">

  <p>
    Dear <strong>Dr. <%= @user.last_name %></strong>,
  </p>

  <p>
    This is an automated reminder that the window for your current
    <strong><%= @pillar_name %></strong> task is closing soon.
  </p>

  <p>
    To maintain the integrity of your data and stay aligned with your custom
    strategy, please upload your proof within the next
    <strong>60 minutes</strong>.
    Consistent adherence is the key to seeing improvements in your
    Oura recovery scores.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">
    How to complete this:
  </p>

  <ol style="padding-left: 20px;">
    <li>Open the Custom Sleep Journey app</li>
    <li>Go to the <strong><%= @pillar_name %></strong> section</li>
    <li>Snap a photo or upload your screenshot and tap <strong>Submit</strong></li>
  </ol>

  <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">
    <strong>Note:</strong>
    If you are currently in an emergency or surgical procedure,
    please disregard this reminder and update your coach as soon as
    you are off-shift.
  </p>

  <%= render "mailers/shared/button",
      text: "Upload Proof Now",
      url: @upload_url %>

  <p style="margin-top: 25px;">
    Stay on track,<br>
    <strong style="color:#0e3264;">
      The My Custom Sleep Journey Team
    </strong>
  </p>
</div>

<%= render "mailers/shared/footer",
    note: "This is an automated reminder. No reply is required.",
    company_name: "My Custom Sleep Journey" %>
